title: TAXII2
description: This is a generic TAXII2 connector for OpenCTI. It automates the importing of collection(s) from a specified TAXII2 2.0 and 2.1 servers.
short_description: This is a generic TAXII2 connector for OpenCTI. It automates the importing of collection(s) from a specified TAXII2 2.0 and 2.1 servers.
